Wasteland 023 (c2c) (2009) (Zone-DCP)


The Marriage that will unite two Dog Tribes is about to take place, and Michael and Abi are running out of time. Gerr has come to rescue them, but they don't know his true agenda. When his ruse is uncovered by the tribes, will he be accepted as an ally? And what will he make of Michael's tale of what he and Abi found?



Many thanks to Zone :)
